{"tid":762731,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PC]連登Don't Starve Together/Board game綜合群","createTime":"2018-07-31T13:59:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T18:48:36.000Z","uid":16945,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1b55a33d5f9edd225d8973c872cd688f1be0516b","tid":762731,"uid":16945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T13:59:48.000Z","msg":"見暫時連登都冇人開discord群玩board game<br />\n所以想招多d人黎玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n入得黎discord群都可以一齊玩，冇小圈子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n玩下draw something,狼人 各式各類ge board game<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/471498679023435776/473512658335957002/unknown.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.discordapp.net%2Fattachments%2F471498679023435776%2F473512658335957002%2Funknown.png&h=70085622&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/471498679023435776/472462591160221697/unknown.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.discordapp.net%2Fattachments%2F471498679023435776%2F472462591160221697%2Funknown.png&h=cb3a728d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另外都推介tabletop Simulator<br />\n有好多種類ge卡game, board game<br />\n可以喺steam度down d workshop item黎玩<br />\n單售大概$119<br />\n買4個copy同朋友分就每人$80度<br />\n<a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/286160/Tabletop_Simulator/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F286160%2FTabletop_Simulator%2F&d=rbotY4UwvtV8%2BbxlHH5kJy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=9c9bf12e\" target=\"_blank\">https://store.steampowered.com/app/286160/Tabletop_Simulator/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/471498679023435776/473524596445020160/20180731001647_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.discordapp.net%2Fattachments%2F471498679023435776%2F473524596445020160%2F20180731001647_1.jpg&h=b359e77d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/470990203633532928/473550167438655488/20180731010102_1.jpg?width=1448&amp;height=815\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.discordapp.net%2Fattachments%2F470990203633532928%2F473550167438655488%2F20180731010102_1.jpg%3Fwidth%3D1448%26height%3D815&h=dec84733&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/470990203633532928/473550198010937364/20180731004920_1.jpg?width=1448&amp;height=815\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.discordapp.net%2Fattachments%2F470990203633532928%2F473550198010937364%2F20180731004920_1.jpg%3Fwidth%3D1448%26height%3D815&h=8e59844e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而我地個discord群本身係Don&rsquo;t Starve together 群黎<br />\nDon't Starve Together就係一隻生存game黎<br />\n畫風幾得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有d怪打下起下base咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/322330/Dont_Starve_Together/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F322330%2FDont_Starve_Together%2F&d=rbotY4UwvtV8%2BbxlHH5kJy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=3dcb031f\" target=\"_blank\">https://store.steampowered.com/app/322330/Dont_Starve_Together/</a><br />\n<br />\n之前d生活照:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/214239_6a885610c52a155e61bdc4b34c74930f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F214239_6a885610c52a155e61bdc4b34c74930f.png&h=e5ad46aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/214250_4fee822cf59558e976df4237e6cbaf3a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F214250_4fee822cf59558e976df4237e6cbaf3a.png&h=65464f85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/214824_c79228784d20cf096ae071712b01cbb5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F214824_c79228784d20cf096ae071712b01cbb5.png&h=f90ac8e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/214831_d0fe492f7f050305129cfa7eadfcfe27.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F214831_d0fe492f7f050305129cfa7eadfcfe27.png&h=8d0d15cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/214838_0631459e921aa3c1928c9387d002cb75.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F214838_0631459e921aa3c1928c9387d002cb75.png&h=9dc1a821&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/214844_bf0cd875626458de782b57903b02f2d1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F214844_bf0cd875626458de782b57903b02f2d1.png&h=b375f25f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上個post: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/630448/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/630448/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n嚟緊我地都會開新地圖,希望有多d新血可以入黎玩呢隻game<br />\n雖然隻game對新手唔friendly,會係咁死<br />\n但上咗手之後會變得好好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外都會玩下其他pc game例如 warfare, l4d2, r6 siege咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n暫時都唔會開tg gp,主要都係喺discord群交流<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\ndiscord群傳送門: <a href=\"https://discord.gg/ZUBn7eT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2FZUBn7eT&d=rbotY4UwvtV8%2BbxlHH5kJy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=5f27681a\" target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/ZUBn7eT</a>"},{"pid":"ac9d19493e51ef3424218380cb42c53f07e187c8","tid":762731,"uid":38131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T14:09:47.000Z","msg":"新手留名學野"},{"pid":"d2862c6e6f85e5ae7e50a49018fef54046fe2ea7","tid":762731,"uid":41006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T14:17:57.000Z","msg":"新手留名學野"},{"pid":"8547e41c1dfb4888db0682cd5d300b331ad728db","tid":762731,"uid":1954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T14:41:29.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"9b6f77cf68dbf2f86b751ed33de4212f9b25dc3e","tid":762731,"uid":16945,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T15:18:29.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8604e9d1703d6f0279779d80004ba2975e324072","tid":762731,"uid":47091,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T15:22:17.000Z","msg":"Pissh"},{"pid":"b0cd1d0c0d3f5fefcaf25b8382d741ecfa36d04e","tid":762731,"uid":16945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T17:41:16.000Z","msg":"DST新手教學1:<br />\n Don&rsquo;t Starve Together係一隻平面向ge生存game。顧名思義，就係唔好餓死，用自己生法去生存<br />\n咁會有三個值黎睇你身體狀況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n心:Hp<br />\n饑餓值:當餓值跌至零，畫面被紅色包住，而且會不斷扣血，直至有野食為止<br />\n入黑冇光源三秒會被扣大半血，下一秒死亡,所以係唔可以冇光<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n腦(sen值):理智值係會比較難明ge一樣野<br />\n當入黑時(黃昏時)理智開始扣<br />\n假如理智低過35，會有影怪(腦魔)追住你黎打，新手會比較難佢地(不過打死佢地會回理智)<br />\n最簡單ge回理智方法就係執地下d花，再用12個花整花圈(喺hat度合)就可以慢慢回理智<br />\n之後仲有一d食譜同工具可以回理智，遲d再教<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n季節:<br />\nDon&rsquo;t starve 世界都會有春夏秋冬<br />\nday1 default setting係秋天，因為秋天係最安全<br />\n秋天: Day1~Day20<br />\n冬天: Day21~Day36<br />\n春天: Day37~Day50<br />\n夏天: Day51~Day69<br />\n<br />\n70日為一個季節cycle.由於呢篇係新手教學，所以就會重點講秋天同冬天生存理論(理據熊貓大師話過咗Day 30先係新手畢業）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nCrafting:<br />\n見到左邊有一行野係用黎俾你craft道具<br />\n武器,咁我會講下每個bar有咁重要道具可以合<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n包括(由上至下):<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/01/000955_dd1895b49f0a1c02663c3d1a4f8958fe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F01%2F000955_dd1895b49f0a1c02663c3d1a4f8958fe.png&h=e96b0455&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n道具:斧頭,pickaxe,Shovel<br />\n火種:火爐,火把,<br />\n生存(背包,心,Trap),<br />\n食物(煮食爐,雪箱),<br />\n科學:呢個好重要,你見到好多野都lock咗唔俾你craft,所以你要起一級Science Machine黎unlock d野<br />\n一旦發明咗之後周街行都可以craft果舊野<br />\nScience Machine可craft ge重要ge野<br />\nBackpack, 煮食爐,木甲,矛,Shovel,二級Science Machine<br />\nAlchemy machine(二級Science Machine):<br />\n可以unlock晒所有crafting物品(Magic除外)<br />\n可craft重要道具:冰箱,二級農田,鳥籠,雪球機etc<br />\n<br />\n武器:矛，木裝甲<br />\n<br />\nStructure建築:箱,鳥籠,豬人屋<br />\n<br />\n鑽石:呢度有三個好重要ge野<br />\n分別係繩(用三個草合<br />\n木板(四舊木)<br />\n石塊(三個木)<br />\n就好似加工品咁，有唔少道具要用佢地黎合<br />\netc,木箱要用3個木板合<br />\n咁就要用12個木合三個木板<br />\n再用3個木板合木箱<br />\n<br />\n木甲log suit ingredient:8個木 ,兩條繩<br />\n咁首先要用6個草合兩條繩<br />\n跟住再去武器度用8個木加兩條繩合件log suit<br />\n<br />\nMagic:可合魔法機(1,2級)，唔係新手教學課程<br />\n<br />\nHat:花環，草帽，top hat,Winter Hat<br />\n<br />\nCharacter:<br />\n共11個character，每個人都有特別技能(個人武器,高血量<br />\n推介用Wilson<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/01/001426_d98b432fe84732723c46d2c5fa564a03.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F01%2F001426_d98b432fe84732723c46d2c5fa564a03.png&h=c89ba056&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因為佢冇負面效果,數值平均,同埋生鬚可以有助喺冬天時保暖<br />\n<br />\n其次推薦wigfrid<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/01/001410_36a567425796f018909c45ffcdf0fb38.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F01%2F001410_36a567425796f018909c45ffcdf0fb38.png&h=60fc4f5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n特性係好打得<br />\n一開始就可以整佢支battle spear同Helemet<br />\n打怪回理智<br />\n缺點：唔食菜(蘿蔔,berry)<br />\n但用berry煮肉丸就ok<br />\n總知就係唔係唔可以直接食生果同菜<br />\n<br />\n快速鍵:<br />\nM=map<br />\nF=打唔friendly ge怪<br />\n空白鍵=執野<br />\ncrt+left click=放低一件野<br />\n<br />\n生存基本要素:<br />\n草<br />\n樹枝<br />\n木頭<br />\n打火石(flint)<br />\n蜘蛛網(silk)<br />\n食物<br />\n<br />\n基本食譜:<br />\n肉丸: 仼何肉(兔肉/怪獸肉)+3x果/菜(berry/冰) +50飽價<br />\n蜜糖小肉: 仼何肉(兔圈/怪獸肉)+1蜂蜜+2x果/菜<br />\n拖肥糖:4x蜂蜜  回理智<br />\n餃子:大肉(怪獸肉)+蛋(餵肉俾雀食)+菜(蘿蔔)+果(berry) 回血<br />\n大蜜糖肉:大肉+怪獸肉+蜜糖+菜/果 回血/飽食<br />\n肉湯:2x大肉+1怪獸肉+1菜果 回滿飽食<br />\n<br />\n詳細食譜:<a href=\"https://bluehexagons.github.io/foodguide/html/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbluehexagons.github.io%2Ffoodguide%2Fhtml%2F&d=rbotY4UwvtV8%2BbxlHH5kJy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=0c1f8cdc\" target=\"_blank\">https://bluehexagons.github.io/foodguide/html/</a>"},{"pid":"fafd30d4c76e9a93c45d2d7594a653b35e10b3fa","tid":762731,"uid":16945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T17:42:09.000Z","msg":"DST新手教學2:<br />\nDay 1~30流程<br />\nday1-5主要係擴張地圖<br />\n(小技巧:夜晚靠燒樹有光源，唔洗起營火)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n主要要揾幾個目標<br />\n1.豬王/豬人村<br />\n提供食物(農作物同，豬人會幫你打怪<br />\n請佢食肉會跟你做野<br />\n包括打怪，砍樹<br />\n佢地死左之後三日就會喺豬屋出返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2.牛群<br />\n出現喺稻草地<br />\n提供大肉,牛毛，號角(其實新手唔應該打佢)<br />\n牛係中立生物<br />\n打一隻就會引起牛群圍毆你<br />\n牛毛可以用黎整冬帽(保暖用)<br />\n收集牛毛方法:<br />\n夜晚去牛群度整個小營火<br />\n拎住個鬚刨，對隻手left click就得<br />\n牛牛最大用處就係做打手，幫手打惡生物<br />\n(蜘蛛，狗)<br />\n但牛會有發情期，屎忽會變紅色<br />\n<br />\n3.沼澤地(紫色地)<br />\n最危險ge地方<br />\n會有觸手彈上黎打人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好處:<br />\n有狗來襲時，揾佢地打<br />\nfarm蜘蛛<br />\n收集d草黎做紙<br />\n觸手死後會掉狼牙棒<br />\n<br />\n4.收集gear<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/01/001105_4fd0dffa2414cb0952fca38d0bdc6b8c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F01%2F001105_4fd0dffa2414cb0952fca38d0bdc6b8c.png&h=6c56400a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n主要都係要打d發條怪黎收集(左)<br />\n如果有教主/西牛就要小心d打(中/右)<br />\n掘墓地有10%出gear<br />\n開草球有1%出<br />\ngear最少要收集1-3個<br />\n一個用黎整雪櫃(保存食物)<br />\n兩個用黎整雪球機(夏天用)<br />\n<br />\n5.海象屋<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/01/002404_e8853fa4e733a4acb2c81c0802f82e56.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F01%2F002404_e8853fa4e733a4acb2c81c0802f82e56.png&h=3d02b49c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n平時只會見到黑色一個洞<br />\n冬天先會出黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/01/002426_a9009d3ab9dcccaffcecb6f56f3ff02c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F01%2F002426_a9009d3ab9dcccaffcecb6f56f3ff02c.png&h=a91b023d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屋會出兩隻冰狗，一隻海象同海象bb<br />\n海象會有機率掉落海象牙同貝雷帽(兩樣都係好珍貴ge物品)<br />\n海象牙可以整Walking Cane 大幅增加移動速度<br />\n貝雷帽保暖加回理智(回得算快)<br />\n海象死後三日先復活，所以一個冬天可以打大約五次<br />\n<br />\n假如揾到晒就可以準備起base<br />\n所需材料(minium):<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/01/001304_1d11bc0d991991aefdfc6814da168c54.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F01%2F001304_1d11bc0d991991aefdfc6814da168c54.png&h=d3fb3e93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n20個果樹<br />\n20個稻草根<br />\n20個樹支根/樹支樹種子<br />\n(三個都係用shovel 挖,要整Science machine物可以<br />\n大量石頭同木頭(約60)<br />\n40粒炭(燒樹獲得)<br />\n<br />\n要起ge設施:<br />\n一級/二級科學機<br />\n4x煮食爐<br />\n1x石營火<br />\n1x雪櫃<br />\n3&lt;存物箱<br />\n1x鳥籠<br />\n2&lt;豬屋<br />\n2&lt;農地<br />\n魔法機(新手optional)<br />\n避雷針<br />\n1x雪球機<br />\n5x蜂箱<br />\n<br />\nbase位置:<br />\n近豬村/牛群(唔可以同佢地一齊住，佢地會發癲/發情)<br />\n有蟲洞可傳送去其他地方<br />\n有兔仔洞<br />\n<br />\n以上面圖為例子:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/01/001222_0c100092b654477541bd4d9ce9b37994.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F01%2F001222_0c100092b654477541bd4d9ce9b37994.png&h=a68b16b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紅圈係豬村<br />\n藍圈係牛村<br />\n綠圈係沼澤<br />\n白圈係base<br />\n黃圈係蟲洞(傳送門)<br />\n<br />\nday6-9<br />\n其中一日會有狗突襲<br />\nbgm有狗聲/角色會講野提你有狗<br />\n唔夠打可以揾豬/牛打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nday10-20<br />\n其中一日月圓，夜晚無需開燈<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/01/001334_a58b5f568854636e3f6636e0aa802ba9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F01%2F001334_a58b5f568854636e3f6636e0aa802ba9.png&h=43eacc4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可以去豬村揾glommer<br />\n但要留意係豬人喺月圓會變痴線打人<br />\n其他時間都係收集食物，資源過冬<br />\n因為冬天唔會出農作物<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nday21<br />\n冬天來臨，記住帶暖石同冬帽出街<br />\n去打海象<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nday22-28<br />\n收集資源，掘下冰(可當食物)殺下兔子<br />\n冰要最少留15舊整雪球機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nday29-day31<br />\n冬王來臨<br />\n聽到呼吸聲立刻離開營地<br />\n(怕營地被破壞可以day29出去起個假營地)<br />\n準備道具:<br />\n2x武器<br />\n2xlog suit<br />\n回血食物<br />\n回理智食物<br />\n1個石營火<br />\n<br />\n冬王係範圍攻擊<br />\n要打兩下就一下咁<br />\n打佢ge時候理智急跌<br />\n有機會出現腦魔黎打你<br />\n同埋要注意保暖(睇個暖石會唔會凍咗)<br />\n基本上都夠打了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n打勝咗就完成新手教學了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大佬死咗會跌眼球，可以整eyebrella(擋雨春天用)"},{"pid":"381595fc1baf46200ccc735dea0fddc73cb9ea7c","tid":762731,"uid":38131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T05:20:05.000Z","msg":"琴晚入左去玩<br />\n有個叫崎三既巴打好好人咁教我地玩boardgame<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39992eca6631187e6f31e5d75e18d067dcf7f4f9","tid":762731,"uid":142787,"like":0,"disl